Check out homepage on googlecode: http://code.google.com/p/javersion/

Include in POM: 

There aren't any official releases yet, but you can add it to your maven project by adding this dependency to your pom's dependency section:

<dependency>
      <groupId>org.restlesscode.javersion</groupId>
      <artifactId>javersion</artifactId>
      <version>1.0.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
</dependency>
And by adding this to the repository section:

<repositories>
    <repository>
      <id>javersionrepo</id>
      <name>javersion repo</name>
      <url>http://javersion.googlecode.com/svn/maven2</url>
    </repository>
</repositories>
